videos.description: Arizona State's Shannon Evans II throws it up to Obinna Oleka who throws down a big time slam over Purdue's P.J. Thompson.
videos.headline: ASU's Oleka goes over the top for one-handed slam

videos.description: 1H (13:25) ASU Torian Graham made Dunk. Assisted by Ramon Vila.

videos.description: Carsen Edwards drains a 3-pointer at the buzzer and Purdue takes a commanding 47-21 lead over Arizona State into the half.
videos.headline: Purdue ends half in style with buzzer beater
